@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001
@adminSecret = replace-with-strong-secret

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

###

### ----- ADMIN ENDPOINTS (require x-security header) -----

### Status (health, observability, runtime snapshot)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/status
x-security: {{adminSecret}}

###

### Stats (trade statistics, paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/stats?page=1&page_size=10
x-security: {{adminSecret}}

###

### Bot Balances (paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/bots/balances?page=1&page_size=10
x-security: {{adminSecret}}

###

### Vault Wallet Balances
GET {{baseUrl}}/admin/vault/balances
x-security: {{adminSecret}}

###

### ----- TRADING -----

### Force Buy Cycle (all markets)
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/bots/buy
x-security: {{adminSecret}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

###

### Force Buy Cycle (specific markets)
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/bots/buy
x-security: {{adminSecret}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "market_ids": ["market-id-here"]
}

###

### Force Sell Cycle (all markets)
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/bots/sell
x-security: {{adminSecret}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

###

### Force Sell Cycle (specific markets)
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/bots/sell
x-security: {{adminSecret}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "market_ids": ["market-id-here"]
}

###

### ----- BOT MANAGEMENT -----

### Add Bots
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/bots/add
x-security: {{adminSecret}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "count": 1
}

###

### Manual Fund (all bots, default token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/bots/fund
x-security: {{adminSecret}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

###

### Manual Fund (specific bots, specific token and amount)
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/bots/fund
x-security: {{adminSecret}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bot_ids": ["bot-id-here"],
  "amount": 100,
  "token": "USDT"
}

###

### ----- MARKET CONTROL -----

### Add Ignored Markets
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/markets/ignored/add
x-security: {{adminSecret}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "market_ids": ["market-id-to-ignore"]
}

###

### Remove Ignored Markets
POST {{baseUrl}}/admin/markets/ignored/remove
x-security: {{adminSecret}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "market_ids": ["market-id-to-unignore"]
}

###

### ----- RUNTIME CONFIG -----

### Update Trading Config
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/config
x-security: {{adminSecret}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "trading": {
    "buyChance": 90,
    "sellChance": 35,
    "maxAmount": 1000,
    "prefundMultiplier": 10
  }
}

###

### Update Funding Config
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/config
x-security: {{adminSecret}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "funding": {
    "emergencyTopupCooldownMs": 60000,
    "minBotSol": 0.01,
    "vaultSupportedTokens": ["USDT", "USDC"]
  }
}

###

### Update Price Policy
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/admin/config
x-security: {{adminSecret}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": {
    "stalePricePolicy": "skip"
  }
}
